snippet.title: My First Commercial Game!
snippet.description:
In this video I talk about the lessons I've learned from my first commercial game A Strange Hotel, and I will answer a few questions about it.

Wishlist A Strange Hotel
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1595950/A_Strange_Hotel/?beta=0

Join our discord: https://discord.gg/6ebpsqtDYa

Watch me on Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/eminspace​​​​

And remember, i am a she, lol.

[timestamps]
0:00​ Intro
1:12 Playtesting
2:20 deadline and scope
4:09 Q&A
7:03 Outro
